-## Usage
-
-Add the following to your `Cargo.toml`:
-
-```toml
-[dependencies]
-lazycell = "1.3"
-```
-
-And in your `lib.rs` or `main.rs`:
-
-```rust
-extern crate lazycell;
-```
-
-See the [API docs][api-docs] for information on using the crate in your library.
