-    // i.e. 1/8/23 (sign, exponent, mantissa)
-    // See https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IEEE_754-1985
-    // n = (sign*-1) * 2^exp * mantissa
-    // Decimal of course stores this differently... 10^-exp * significand
